WWE makes an example out of the former Ridge Holland by cutting off his remaining pay after he posted online about feeling hung out to dry when he was released in the middle of recovery.  
  
AEW Blood and Guts hasn't happened yet but the injuries are piling up!  
  
Another championship belt?! AEW introduces a National Championship that sounds a lot like the original concept for the International Championship  
  
We have to talk about WWE creative in 2025  
  
